<title>USA: Triangle Banc to buy Bank of Mecklenburg.</title>
<headline>Triangle Banc to buy Bank of Mecklenburg.</headline>
<dateline>RALEIGH, N.C. 1997-03-28</dateline>
<text>
<p>Triangle Bancorp Inc. on Friday said it executed a letter of intent to acquire all of the capital stock of Bank of Mecklenburg in Charlotte, North Carolina.</p>
<p>As of December 31, Bank of Mecklenburg reported total assets of $270 million. At the completion of the merger, Triangle will have assets in excess of $1.2 billion.</p>
